These files are matlab implementation of the adaptive edge weighting 
method for label propagation proposed in "Manifold-based similarity
adaptation for label propagation", by M. Karasuyama and H. Mamitsuka
(NIPS 2013).

Important files
[test_run1.m]: A test script to run the method with synthetic data used in the above paper.
[AEW.m]: Optimizing edge weights for subsequent label propagation.
[HGF.m]: Label propagation by the harmonic Gaussian field model